Pekao May Grant 6 Billion Zloty of Mortgages in 2011, PAP Says

-- B y   P a w e l   K o z l o w s k i
-- 
2011-06-09T11:32:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/pekao-may-grant-6-billion-zloty-of-mortgages-in-2011-pap-says.html
Bank Pekao SA (PEO) , Poland’s second-
largest bank, plans to grant more than 6 billion zloty ($2.2
billion) in home loans in 2011, PAP newswire reported today,
citing Remigiusz Falkowski, who heads the bank’s mortgage loan
department.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pawel Kozlowski in Warsaw 
 pkozlowski@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  